						<div class="postbody">Null = 0.<br /><br />Null pointer points to address  $0000.<br /><br />I don't know if the scenario you mentioned is possible. But it seems like an unusual situation... having a valid pointer to the zero page address zero. Hmm.<br /><br />You would think cc65 would give an error message if you tried to do this.</div>

					
